sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as /api/news
    participant Pagination
    participant Guardian
    participant NewsData
    participant Currents

    Client->>API: GET /api/news

    API->>Guardian: Fetch page 1
    API->>NewsData: Fetch cursor null
    API->>Currents: Fetch page 1

    Guardian-->>API: Articles + next page=2
    NewsData-->>API: Articles + next cursor="abc123"
    Currents-->>API: Articles + next page=2

    API->>Pagination: Build composite state

    Note over Pagination: {guardianPage:2,<br/>newsDataCursor:"abc123",<br/>currentsPage:2,<br/>timestamp:t1}

    Pagination->>Pagination: Encode cursor
    Pagination-->>API: eyJndWFyZGlhblBhZ2UiOjIs...

    API-->>Client: Articles + nextPage token

    Client->>API: GET /api/news?page=eyJndWFy...

    API->>Pagination: Decode token

    Note over Pagination: Validate timestamp<br/>Reject if expired

    Note over Pagination: {guardianPage:2,<br/>newsDataCursor:"abc123",<br/>currentsPage:2}

    Pagination-->>API: Restored provider state

    API->>Guardian: Fetch page 2
    API->>NewsData: Fetch cursor "abc123"
    API->>Currents: Fetch page 2

    Guardian-->>API: Next batch
    NewsData-->>API: Next batch
    Currents-->>API: Next batch

    API-->>Client: Articles + new nextPage token
